flowRoot.flowPara: With all patrons at the base pledge of 1 share, your input receives nearly 1:1 matching from the other patrons.
A double pledge (2 shares), counts like 2 patrons (i.e. share-value goes up 0.2¢).
The rate of matching from others is slightly reduced because you are now also matching yourself.
At a quadruple pledge, your 4 shares get matched like 3 base-level patrons (share-value increases 0.3¢).
For each additional patron who joins, the share value for everyone goes up by 0.1¢.
Thus, each extra 0.1¢ that one patron adds is itself matched many times over.
For each doubling of your pledge, everyone's shares go up by 0.1¢.
An 8-share pledge gets matched like 4 base-level patrons (share-value increases 0.4¢).
A 16-share pledge gets matched like 5 base-level patrons (share-value increases 0.5¢),
